_sText:
This map is a complete overhaul of the original complete with fixed traps, some new ones, and most importantly GRAPHICS OVERHAUL.  There isn't much left for me to say about the map except that I hope you enjoy it as much as I did. =]  

Note: Ts must push the last trap on a floor to advance to the next, and yes this is intentional.

V3 update-
Fixed some bugs and added breaking glass for players who take too long.
